                        <h1 class="head1">Payment Information</h1>
                        <p>At TechCraft, we aim to make your online shopping experience seamless and enjoyable. We offer several simple payment options tailored around your convenience.</p>
                
                        <h2 class="head2">Cash on Delivery</h2>
                        <p>For straightforward transactions, choose "Cash on Delivery" at checkout. You'll receive a confirmation call before delivery to prepare the payment.</p>
                
                        <h2 class="head2">Online Bank Transfer</h2>
                        <p>Prefer online transactions? Select "Bank Transfer" during checkout and follow the instructions to transfer from your bank account.</p>
                
                        <h2 class="head2">Direct Bank Deposits</h2>
                        <p>You can also deposit your payment directly at our partnering banks. Visit any of our listed banks to make your payment directly.</p>
                
                        <h2 class="head2">ATM Transfers</h2>
                        <p>Conveniently use your ATM card to make payments at any nearby ATM.</p>
                
                        <h2 class="head2">FonePay Payment</h2>
                        <p>Use the FonePay app to link various payment methods including bank accounts and mobile wallets for quick payments.</p>
                
                        <p><strong>Note:</strong> For certain orders, TechCraft may require an advance payment to confirm your purchase.</p>
                
                        <h2 class="head2">Refund Process</h2>
                        <p>If an order is cancelled due to unforeseen circumstances, you are entitled to a full refund, which will be processed within 3-7 working days.</p>
                
                        <p>For more details on our payment methods, contact our support team at <a href="mailto:info@techcraft.com">info@techcraft.com</a> or call (+92) 3 111 000 135.</p>
